The '''Spice Berry''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] found via [[foraging]] in the [[Summer]] or grown from [[Summer Seeds]]. Putting a Spice Berry in a [[Seed Maker]] will generate 1-3 [[Summer Seeds]].

